public static class ContactMethodTypeTable.EnumeratedItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements EnumeratedItem

This class represents a cache of the enumerated values from the Contact_Method_Type table. It is designed to allow access to the actual values stored in the database without having to retrieve the data from the database each time it's needed (for example, you would use this class to check the caption of an enumerated item without doing a join in the database).
